snippet.description:
PUBG Mobile Global Championship 2023 League Stage ko Group Green Day 4 suru hune samaya bhaisakeko chha. PMGC 2023 Final ma afno sthan banauna World bhari ka top team haru bich hune kada competition hamile dekhna paaune chau!

2023 PMGC Format ko barema janna tapai sabai interested ta hunu huncha hola, so here are some key points:
- PMGC 2023 ko League Stage 4-week event hunecha, ra yo stage bata qualify hune top team haru İstanbul, Türkiye ma Decemeber 8 dekhi 10 samma hune PMGC Grand Finals ko lagi qualify hunechan.
- Sahabhagi 48 team haru lai group draw ka adhar ma Green, Red ra Yellow gari 3 groups ma badhine cha, ra team haru yehi group bhitra compete garne chhan.
- Harek group ko Top 3 teams direct Finals ko lagi qualify hune chhan.
- 4th dekhi 11th position ka team haru Survival stage ma prabesh garne chhan, ra baki ko team competition bata bahirine chhan.
-  Baki raheka 24 ota team compete garne chhan ra tyaha bata Top 16 team PMGC League: Last Chance ko lagi qualify hunechan.
- Last Chance bata Top 5 teams Ülker Sports & Event Hall, İstanbul ma hune Grand Finals ko lagi qualify hune chhan. 

Join us and don't miss the action!  Group Green bata kun kun team Top 3 ma finish garchhan hola ta? Afno guess hamilai comments ma bhannuhos!

The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.title: [NP] 2023 PMGC League | Group Green Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
PUBG Mobile Global Championship 2023 League Stage ko Group Green Day 1 suru hune samaya bhaisakeko chha. PMGC 2023 Final ma afno sthan banauna World bhari ka top team haru bich hune kada competition hamile dekhna paaune chau!

2023 PMGC Format ko barema janna tapai sabai interested ta hunu huncha hola, so here are some key points:
- PMGC 2023 ko League Stage 4-week event hunecha, ra yo stage bata qualify hune top team haru İstanbul, Türkiye ma Decemeber 8 dekhi 10 samma hune PMGC Grand Finals ko lagi qualify hunechan.
- Sahabhagi 48 team haru lai group draw ka adhar ma Green, Red ra Yellow gari 3 groups ma badhine cha, ra team haru yehi group bhitra compete garne chhan.
- Harek group ko Top 3 teams direct Finals ko lagi qualify hune chhan.
- 4th dekhi 11th position ka team haru Survival stage ma prabesh garne chhan, ra baki ko team competition bata bahirine chhan.
-  Baki raheka 24 ota team compete garne chhan ra tyaha bata Top 16 team PMGC League: Last Chance ko lagi qualify hunechan.
- Last Chance bata Top 5 teams Ülker Sports & Event Hall, İstanbul ma hune Grand Finals ko lagi qualify hune chhan. 

Join us and don't miss the action!  Group Green bata kun kun team Top 3 ma finish garchhan hola ta? Afno guess hamilai comments ma bhannuhos!

snippet.title: [NP] 2023 PMGC League | Group Green Day 2 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
PUBG Mobile Global Championship 2023 League Stage ko Group Green Day 2 suru hune samaya bhaisakeko chha. PMGC 2023 Final ma afno sthan banauna World bhari ka top team haru bich hune kada competition hamile dekhna paaune chau!

2023 PMGC Format ko barema janna tapai sabai interested ta hunu huncha hola, so here are some key points:
- PMGC 2023 ko League Stage 4-week event hunecha, ra yo stage bata qualify hune top team haru İstanbul, Türkiye ma Decemeber 8 dekhi 10 samma hune PMGC Grand Finals ko lagi qualify hunechan.
- Sahabhagi 48 team haru lai group draw ka adhar ma Green, Red ra Yellow gari 3 groups ma badhine cha, ra team haru yehi group bhitra compete garne chhan.
- Harek group ko Top 3 teams direct Finals ko lagi qualify hune chhan.
- 4th dekhi 11th position ka team haru Survival stage ma prabesh garne chhan, ra baki ko team competition bata bahirine chhan.
-  Baki raheka 24 ota team compete garne chhan ra tyaha bata Top 16 team PMGC League: Last Chance ko lagi qualify hunechan.
- Last Chance bata Top 5 teams Ülker Sports & Event Hall, İstanbul ma hune Grand Finals ko lagi qualify hune chhan. 

Join us and don't miss the action!  Group Green bata kun kun team Top 3 ma finish garchhan hola ta? Afno guess hamilai comments ma bhannuhos!

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/PMGCLive2023

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.
